    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <h2>thoughtfulchatsandhealthub</h2>
    
    <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> July 12, 2025</p>
    
    <h3>Information We Collect</h3>
    <p>This application automatically posts video content to Instagram from Google Drive. We only access:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Video files from your Google Drive for posting purposes</li>
        <li>Instagram posting permissions to publish content to your account</li>
        <li>Basic Instagram profile information required for authentication</li>
    </ul>
    
    <h3>How We Use Information</h3>
    <p>We use the accessed information solely to:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Retrieve video files from your Google Drive</li>
        <li>Post videos to your Instagram account automatically</li>
        <li>Maintain posting schedules and track posted content</li>
    </ul>
    
    <h3>Data Storage and Security</h3>
    <p>We do not store any personal data, videos, or Instagram content on our servers. All processing is done in real-time through the automation workflow. Temporary access tokens are handled securely and not logged.</p>
    
    <h3>Third-Party Services</h3>
    <p>This application integrates with:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Google Drive API - for accessing your video files</li>
        <li>Instagram Basic Display API - for posting content</li>
        <li>n8n automation platform - for workflow execution</li>
    </ul>
    
    <h3>Your Rights</h3>
    <p>You can revoke access to this application at any time through your Google and Instagram account settings.</p>
    
    <div class="contact">
        <h3>Contact Information</h3>
        <p>For any questions about this Privacy Policy, contact us at: <strong>svijayaravindan@gmail.com</strong></p>
    </div>
